sql_json.natural_language: Pull all emails with attachments in the last 30 days.
sql_json.generated_sql: SELECT messageId, threadId, fromEmail, subject, sentAt, snippet FROM email_search_index WHERE hasAttachments = true AND sentAt >= TIMESTAMP_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL 30 DAY) ORDER BY sentAt DESC LIMIT 1;
